<plot>Simon, an agent at the Department of Weights and Measures looks back on his time spent as a weight guesser at the circus and his relationship with an aspiring fortune teller, Miriam. As their relationship progresses so does Simon's abilities to accurately guess weights. However, their relationship is headed for a dramatic conclusion when Simon must weigh his love for Miriam against his desire to fulfill his father's expectations to become an agent at the Department of Weights and Measures.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?057332</url></doc>
